n"=>"Intel Core i5 3337U (1.80GHz) 4GB Memory 128GB SSD Intel HD Graphics 4000 1920 x 1080 Windows 8 Pro 64-bit","image_url"=>"http://images10.newegg.com/ProductImageCompressAll300/0EJ-001J-00004-01.jpg", "category_name" =>"Electronics", "merchant_name"=>"NewEgg"}, {"title" =>"The Portlandia Activity Book", "price"=>23,"link"=>"https://store.mcsweeneys.net/products/the-portlandia-activity-book","description"=>"This is The Portlandia Activity Book—a compendium of guaranteed enrichment for the Pacific Northwestern part of your psyche. Like a cool high school that prefers a sweat lodge to the traditional classroom, this book will expand your mind through participation, dehydrate you to a state of emotional rawness, then linger in the corners your bare soul.","image_url"=>"https://ddkpmexz7bq23.cloudfront.net/images/production/1667/2014-01-08%2013:33:25%20-0800/product/portlandia_cover_FINAL_STORE.jpg?1389216805", "category_name" =>"Books", "merchant_name"=>"McSweeney's"}, {"title" =>"Ten Years in the Tub", "price"=>26,"link"=>"https://store.mcsweeneys.net/products/ten-years-in-the-tub","description"=>"In late 2003, as the first issue of the Believer magazine was rising from the primordial ooze, Nick Hornby turned in the inaugural installment of a monthly column that immediately became a reader favorite.","image_url"=>"https://ddkpmexz7bq23.cloudfront.net/images/production/1586/2013-11-05%2016:51:06%20-0800/product/thetub_jacket_FINAL_PR.jpg?1383699066","category_name" =>"Books", "merchant_name"=>"McSweeney's"}, {"title" =>"High Rise Stories: Voices from Chicago Public Housing", "price"=>13,"link"=>"https://store.mcsweeneys.net/products/high-rise-stories-voices-from-chicago-public-housing","description"=>"In the gripping first-person accounts of High Rise Stories, former residents of Chicago’s iconic public housing projects describe life in the now-demolished high-rises. These stories of community, displacement, and poverty in the wake of gentrification give voice to those who have long been ignored, but whose hopes and struggles exist firmly at the heart of our national identity.","image_url"=>"https://ddkpmexz7bq23.cloudfront.net/images/production/1464/2013-08-05%2009:35:08%20-0700/large/hrs_cover_FINAL.jpg?1375720508", "category_name" =>"Books","merchant_name"=>"McSweeney's"}, {"title" =>"Phoenix Rising", "category_name" =>"Video Games","price"=>6.95,"link"=>"http://www.lushusa.com/Phoenix-Rising/03575,en_US,pd.html","description"=>"This Bath Bomb is a tribute to our belief that great things can rise out of the ashes, just like the mythical Phoenix. Royal purple and gold-dusted, with a cinnamon stick in the center, this gorgeous bomb sinks to the bottom of the tub when you toss it in, and slowly rises up, fizzing out a spicy apple and cinnamon scent.","image_url"=>"http://demandware.edgesuite.net/sits_pod18/dw/image/v2/AAHL_PRD/on/demandware.static/Sites-Lush-Site/Sites-lushcosmetics-export/en_US/v1394236818157/images/product/03575.jpg?sw=600", "category_name" =>"Cosmetics", "merchant_name"=>"Lush"}, {"title" =>"Roots", "price"=>19.95,"link"=>"http://www.lushusa.com/Roots/03741,en_US,pd.html","description"=>"Fine, thin hair? Don't despair! We've got a hair and scalp treatment just for you. You'll feel the tingling and cooling sensations of fresh mint infusion and minty oils (peppermint and spearmint) as they go to work revitalizing the scalp, because healthy hair starts at the roots! Extra virgin olive oil and honey soften and condition hair to make it shine without weighing it down. Give dull, fine and thin hair volume and shine by treating it with Roots.","image_url"=>"http://demandware.edgesuite.net/sits_pod18/dw/image/v2/AAHL_PRD/on/demandware.static/Sites-Lush-Site/Sites-lushcosmetics-export/en_US/v1394236818157/images/product/03741.jpg?sw=300", "category_name" =>"Cosmetics", "merchant_name"=>"Lush"}, {"title" =>"Skin Sin", "price"=>29.95,"link"=>"http://www.lushusa.com/Skin-Sin/9999902408,en_US,pd.html","description"=>"Wh