tant coating. The chain is a 28in gold plated link. Lobster clasp.","image_url"=>"https://img0.etsystatic.com/000/0/5636223/il_570xN.195234482.jpg","category_name" =>"Jewelry", "merchant_name"=>"Etsy"}, {"title" =>"The Unofficial Game of Thrones Cookbook", "price"=>21.99,"link"=>"http://www.thinkgeek.com/product/ed95/","description"=>"From Direwolf Ale to Auroch Stew!","image_url"=>"http://a.tgcdn.net/images/products/frontsquare/ed95_unofficial_game_of_thrones_cookbook.jpg", "category_name" =>"Books", "merchant_name"=>"ThinkGeek"}, {"title" =>"The ThinkGeek 8-bit Tie", "price"=>19.99,"link"=>"http://www.thinkgeek.com/product/9352/","description"=>"Stylish clip-on tie with 8-bit pixelated design","image_url"=>"http://a.tgcdn.net/images/products/frontsquare/9352_8_bit_tie.jpg", "category_name" =>"Clothing", "merchant_name"=>"ThinkGeek"}, {"title" =>"Octopus Cardigan", "price"=>49.99,"link"=>"http://www.thinkgeek.com/product/f14d/","description"=>"No, no, not a cardigan FOR an octopus. This one only has two arms, so it's for a human. Of course, if you knew a cold octopus, this could warm two of its limbs.","image_url"=>"http://a.tgcdn.net/images/products/frontsquare/f14d_octopus_cardigan.jpg", "category_name" =>"Clothing", "merchant_name"=>"ThinkGeek"}, {"title" =>"Game of Thrones Vinyl Figures Khal Drogo and Dany Wedding Set", "price"=>19.99,"link"=>"http://www.thinkgeek.com/product/1936/","description"=>"Khal and Khaleesi vinyl figures from Funko's Pop! line","image_url"=>"http://a.tgcdn.net/images/products/frontsquare/1936_khal_khaleesi_wedding_vinyl.jpg", "category_name" =>"Toys", "merchant_name"=>"ThinkGeek"}, {"title" =>"So Games Much Thrones Wow Tote", "price"=>12,"link"=>"http://shirt.woot.com/offers/so-games-much-thrones-wow-tote","description"=>"","image_url"=>"http://d3gqasl9vmjfd8.cloudfront.net/fe490928-e646-4ff8-8a4d-c42c6eefccef.png","category_name" =>"Accessories", "merchant_name"=>"Woot"}]
items.each do |item_info|
	m = Merchant.find_by :name=>item_info['merchant_name']
	c = Category.find_by :name=>item_info['category_name']
	i = Item.new
	i.title = item_info['title']
	i.link = item_info['link']
	i.price = item_info['price']
	i.description = item_info['description']
	i.image_url = item_info['image_url']
	i.merchant_id = m.id
	i.category_id = c.id
	i.save
end